data.title: Yorkton Land
data.meta_description: Search Shindico's commercial real estate property listings
data.text:
Land for Sale in Yorkton, Saskatchewan, adjacent to Walmart Supercentre. Ideal for commercial, multifamily, hotel, industrial, and office uses.

Excellent sight lines to Highway #9. Yorkton serves as the main shopping hub for much of east-central Saskatchewan and western Manitoba. Yorkton is the third largest trade area in Saskatchewan, serving much of east-central Saskatchewan and western Manitoba.

Easy access from Trans Canada Yellowhead Highway #16. Yorkton is the largest city on the Trans Canada Yellowhead Highway between Winnipeg, Manitoba and Saskatoon, Saskatchewan. Located on the mainline of the Canadian Pacific Railway and the Bay Line, connected to Churchill, Manitoba.
